<P>He did not [di&s;own] <HI>deny</HI> it.</P>
<P>[To] <HI>by</HI> who&s;e kindne&s;s it is not unlikely that he was [indebted for] <HI>advanced to</HI> his benefices.</P>
<P>[With] <HI>for</HI> this purpo&s;e he had recour&s;e to Mr. Harley.</P>
<P>Sharpe, whom he [repre&s;ents] <HI>de&s;cribes</HI> as <Q REND="inline">'the harmle&s;s tool of others hate.'</Q></P>
